** instructions for guess the number game **
- This game is about guessing a randomly generated number.
- Each time the game is started. A random number is generated, you have 100 chances to guess the number.
- You will be provided with Hints, related to the number you entered. The game will guide you with hints like -> "The Number you entered is Less/Greater than the number you entered".
- The more chances you opt, the lower the score will be.
- At the end of the game you will be provided with the Scores out of 100, which is dependent on the number of attempts.
